 add reminders, capture ideas, write notes, search your knowledge, update projects and automate repetitive work.","zh":"只需自然地交谈即可安排会议、添加提醒、捕捉想法、写笔记、搜索知识、更新项目并自动执行重复性工作。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Free</p>","sentences":[]},{"html_en":"<p>Launch Team </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Launch Team","zh":"发射团队"}]},{"html_en":"<p>/ Built With</p>","sentences":[{"en":"/ Built With","zh":"/ 内置"}]}],"translated":true,"content_html_zh":"<div class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div data-test=\"launch\"><div><p>这是 Routine 的第五次发射。</p><a href=\"/products/routine/launches\"><span>View more</span> <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"17\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 17\"><path stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.667\" d=\"M3.334 8.909h9.333m0 0L8.001 4.242m4.666 4.667-4.666 4.666\" /></svg></a></div><div><div><h2>人工智能套路</h2><p>本周推出</p></div><p>用你的声音控制工作。 工作用的 Siri。</p></div><p>Routine AI 可让您使用语音控制任务、日历、笔记和项目。 只需自然地交谈即可安排会议、添加提醒、捕捉想法、写笔记、搜索知识、更新项目并自动执行重复性工作。</p><div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"44\" height=\"45\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 44 45\"><g filter=\"url(#ChevronRight_svg__a)\"><path fill=\"#fff\" fill-opacity=\"0.9\" d=\"M0 22.614c0-12.15 9.85-22 22-22s22 9.85 22 22-9.85 22-22 22-22-9.85-22-22\" /><path stroke=\"#344054\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"m19 28.614 6-6-6-6\" /></g><defs><filter id=\"ChevronRight_svg__a\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" x=\"-8\" y=\"-7.386\" color-interpolation-filters=\"sRGB\" filterUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\"><feflood flood-opacity=\"0\" result=\"BackgroundImageFix\" /><fegaussianblur in=\"BackgroundImageFix\" stdDeviation=\"4\" /><fecomposite in2=\"SourceAlpha\" operator=\"in\" result=\"effect1_backgroundBlur_5592_12221\" /><feblend in=\"SourceGraphic\" in2=\"effect1_backgroundBlur_5592_12221\" result=\"shape\" /></filter></defs></svg><section><div aria-label=\"Routine AI gallery media\"><svg xmlns=\"http://w